K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-0: @134b dug zhi bar byed pa zhes bya ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-1: bdud rtsi sman gyi lha mo nor gyi rgyun la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-3: aom su ru su ru ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-7: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi bden pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-8: gzi brjid kyis klu'i dug dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-13: gcan gzan mche ba'i dug bcom mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-14: dug nges par bcom mo zhes brjod par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-028:134b-15: dug thams cad zhi bar byed pa'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
